{"id":43,"parent_id":30,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":43,"title":"2 Nephi 13","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Ne.","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 13"],[".studySummary",["i","Judah and Jerusalem will be punished for their disobedience—The Lord pleads for and judges His people—The daughters of Zion are cursed and tormented for their worldliness—Compare",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/3"},"Isaiah 3"],". About 559–545",["span.small","B.C."]]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.1","order":"05.13.013.4792"},["b","1"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"For"],"behold, the Lord, the Lord of Hosts, doth take away from Jerusalem, and from Judah, the stay and the staff, the whole staff of bread, and the whole stay of water—"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.2","order":"05.13.013.4793"},["b","2"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"mighty"],"man, and the man of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"war"],", the judge, and the prophet, and the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"prudent"],", and the ancient;"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.3","order":"05.13.013.4794"},["b","3"],"The captain of fifty, and the honorable man, and the counselor, and the cunning artificer, and the eloquent orator."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.4","order":"05.13.013.4795"},["b","4"],"And I will give children unto them to be their princes, and babes shall rule over them."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.5","order":"05.13.013.4796"},["b","5"],"And the people shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"oppressed"],", every one by another, and every one by his neighbor; the child shall behave himself",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"proudly"],"against the ancient, and the base against the honorable."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.6","order":"05.13.013.4797"},["b","6"],"When a man shall take hold of his brother of the house of his father, and shall say: Thou hast clothing, be thou our ruler, and let not this",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"ruin"],"come under thy hand—"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.7","order":"05.13.013.4798"},["b","7"],"In that day shall he swear, saying: I will not be a healer; for in my house there is neither bread nor clothing; make me not a ruler of the people."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.8","order":"05.13.013.4799"},["b","8"],"For Jerusalem is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"ruined"],", and Judah is",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"fallen"],", because their",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"tongues"],"and their doings have been against the Lord, to",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_8d"},"provoke"],"the eyes of his glory."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.9","order":"05.13.013.4800"},["b","9"],"The show of their countenance doth witness against them, and doth declare their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"sin"],"to be even as",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"Sodom"],", and they cannot hide it. Wo unto their souls, for they have rewarded evil unto themselves!"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.10","order":"05.13.013.4801"},["b","10"],"Say unto the righteous that it is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"well"],"with them; for they shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"eat"],"the fruit of their doings."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.11","order":"05.13.013.4802"},["b","11"],"Wo unto the wicked, for they shall perish; for the reward of their hands shall be upon them!"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.12","order":"05.13.013.4803"},["b","12"],"And my people, children are their oppressors, and women rule over them. O my people, they who",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"lead"],"thee cause thee to err and destroy the way of thy paths."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.13","order":"05.13.013.4804"},["b","13"],"The Lord standeth up to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"plead"],", and standeth to judge the people."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.14","order":"05.13.013.4805"},["b","14"],"The Lord will enter into",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"judgment"],"with the ancients of his people and the princes thereof; for ye have eaten up the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"vineyard"],"and the spoil of the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"poor"],"in your houses."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.15","order":"05.13.013.4806"},["b","15"],"What mean ye? Ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"beat"],"my people to pieces, and grind the faces of the poor, saith the Lord God of Hosts."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.16","order":"05.13.013.4807"},["b","16"],"Moreover, the Lord saith: Because the daughters of Zion are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"haughty"],", and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"walk"],"with stretched-forth necks and wanton eyes, walking and mincing as they go, and making a tinkling with their feet—"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.17","order":"05.13.013.4808"},["b","17"],"Therefore the Lord will smite with a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"scab"],"the crown of the head of the daughters of Zion, and the Lord will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"discover"],"their secret parts."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.18","order":"05.13.013.4809"},["b","18"],"In that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"day"],"the Lord will take away the bravery of their tinkling ornaments, and cauls, and round tires like the moon;"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.19","order":"05.13.013.4810"},["b","19"],"The chains and the bracelets, and the mufflers;"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.20","order":"05.13.013.4811"},["b","20"],"The bonnets, and the ornaments of the legs, and the headbands, and the tablets, and the ear-rings;"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.21","order":"05.13.013.4812"},["b","21"],"The rings, and nose jewels;"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.22","order":"05.13.013.4813"},["b","22"],"The changeable suits of apparel, and the mantles, and the wimples, and the crisping-pins;"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.23","order":"05.13.013.4814"},["b","23"],"The glasses, and the fine linen, and hoods, and the veils."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.24","order":"05.13.013.4815"},["b","24"],"And it shall come to pass, instead of sweet smell there shall be stink; and instead of a girdle, a rent; and instead of well set hair,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"baldness"],"; and instead of a stomacher, a girding of sackcloth;",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"burning"],"instead of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_24c"},"beauty"],"."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.25","order":"05.13.013.4816"},["b","25"],"Thy men shall fall by the sword and thy mighty in the war."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.26","order":"05.13.013.4817"},["b","26"],"And her",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"gates"],"shall lament and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"mourn"],"; and she shall be desolate, and shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_26c"},"sit"],"upon the ground."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.1a","order":"05.13.013.4818"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/3.1.1-26"},"Isa. 3:1 (1–26)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.2a","order":"05.13.013.4820"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/24.14"},"2 Kgs. 24:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.2b","order":"05.13.013.4822"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/28.3"},"1 Chr. 28:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.2c","order":"05.13.013.4824"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prudence"},"TG Prudence"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.5a","order":"05.13.013.4826"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/oppression"},"TG Oppression"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.5b","order":"05.13.013.4828"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/haughtiness"},"TG Haughtiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.6a","order":"05.13.013.4830"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/3.6"},"Isa. 3:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.8a","order":"05.13.013.4832"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/1.7"},"Isa. 1:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.11"},"Jer. 9:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/36.17.16-20"},"Ezek. 36:17 (16–20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.8b","order":"05.13.013.4834"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.3.1-3"},"Lam. 1:3 (1–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.8c","order":"05.13.013.4836"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/52.2"},"Ps. 52:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"8d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.8d","order":"05.13.013.4838"},["b","8d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/provoking"},"TG Provoking"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.9a","order":"05.13.013.4840"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-israel"},"TG Apostasy of Israel"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.9b","order":"05.13.013.4842"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/18.20.20-21"},"Gen. 18:20 (20–21)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/19.5,24.24-25"},"19:5, 24 (24–25)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.19"},"2 Ne. 23:19"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/homosexual-behavior"},"TG Homosexual Behavior"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.10a","order":"05.13.013.4844"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/12.28"},"Deut. 12:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.10b","order":"05.13.013.4846"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/128.2"},"Ps. 128:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.12a","order":"05.13.013.4848"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/9.16"},"Isa. 9:16"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/leadership"},"TG Leadership"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.13a","order":"05.13.013.4850"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/micah/6.2"},"Micah 6:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.14a","order":"05.13.013.4852"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-judge"},"TG Jesus Christ, Judge"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.14b","order":"05.13.013.4854"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/5.7"},"Isa. 5:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.14c","order":"05.13.013.4856"},["b","14c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.12"},"Ezek. 18:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/28.13.12-13"},"2 Ne. 28:13 (12–13)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/4.12.11-13"},"Hel. 4:12 (11–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.15a","order":"05.13.013.4858"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/micah/3.3.2-3"},"Micah 3:3 (2–3)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/26.20"},"2 Ne. 26:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.16a","order":"05.13.013.4860"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/haughtiness"},"TG Haughtiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.16b","order":"05.13.013.4862"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-in-darkness"},"TG Walking in Darkness"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.17a","order":"05.13.013.4864"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/28.27"},"Deut. 28:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.17b","order":"05.13.013.4866"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/13.22"},"Jer. 13:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/3.5"},"Nahum 3:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.18a","order":"05.13.013.4868"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/day-of-the-lord"},"TG Day of the Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.24a","order":"05.13.013.4870"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/22.12"},"Isa. 22:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/micah/1.16"},"Micah 1:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.24b","order":"05.13.013.4872"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/14.4"},"2 Ne. 14:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"24c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.24c","order":"05.13.013.4874"},["b","24c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.6.4-6"},"Lam. 1:6 (4–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.26a","order":"05.13.013.4876"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.2"},"Jer. 14:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"26b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.26b","order":"05.13.013.4878"},["b","26b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.4.4-6"},"Lam. 1:4 (4–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"26c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.26c","order":"05.13.013.4880"},["b","26c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.10"},"Lam. 2:10"],"."]]}
